features: TREAT EVERY WOUND WITH CARE: This top quality medical tape comes in handy in a great variety of situations, which is why you should keep it in your home, office or car at all times. Simply equip your first aid kit with a few of these and you know you are ready for anything that comes your way. Perfect for the healthcare clinic, the hospital, the office, home or vet clinic.

TAILOR TO YOUR NEEDS: Boasting versatility and efficiency, these clear, adhesive surgical tape is extremely strong and yet very gentle on the skin. It will stick to anything and can be used not only for dressing wounds and keeping bandages in place, but also for securing a variety of medical devices, such as catheters, IV tubings etc. What is more, it can easily be cut to your desired size, both across or lengthwise, even with your gloves on.

HYPOALLERGENIC CARE FOR SENSITIVE SKIN: This transparent bandage tape features tiny pores that cover the surface of the tape like a small grid-like pattern and make it extremely breathable. This means that it allows any sweat and body fluid to easily pass through it without causing it to come off. Ideal for sensitive skin, it does not cause any discomfort. [Size: 1" x 10 Yards]

INSPECT THE SKIN AROUND THE WOUND: Conveniently packaged in 12 rolls, our transparent medical tape offers one more advantage: Its clear design allows you to monitor the wound and skin underneath at all times. This makes it easy to watch how the wound is healing, without having to take the tape off. It also allows the air to reach the skin and wound underneath it, thus permitting proper tissue repair.

ORDER WITH PEACE OF MIND: Medpride is your trusted supplier of effective, top quality medical products that you can count on to equip your personal or professional medical kit. Backed by a 30-Day Money Back Guarantee, you have every good reason to choose Medpride for all your medical supplies!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2019
reviews.reviewText: I use transdermal medicated patches that last for 48 hours. I wear the patches during the day and take them off at night, and re-use the patches for a second day. Unfortunately, on day 2, the adhesive isn't as effective as it needs to be, so I purchased this clear tape to keep it on when it is being re-used. I like that it is clear and I like that it stands up to water.Highly recommended!
